‚úÖ UPDATED app.css (THIS FIXES EVERYTHING)

/* APP CONTAINER */
.container {
  height: 100vh;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  background: #f9fdf9;
  font-family: "Poppins", sans-serif;
}

/* FIXED HEADER - hides content under it */
.header {
  position: fixed;
  top: 0;
  left: 0;
  width: 100%;
  height: 80px;
  background-color: #008e5c;  /* solid background = hides content */
  color: white;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: center;
  padding: 10px 20px;
  z-index: 1000;
}

/* FLOATING BUTTON WRAPPER ‚Äî allows pass-through scrolling */
.floating-menu-button-wrapper {
  position: fixed;
  top: 90px;      /* below header */
  left: 15px;
  z-index: 2000;
  pointer-events: none;   /* important: content visible underneath */
}

/* This element captures the click, NOT the wrapper */
.floating-menu-button {
  pointer-events: auto;   /* makes button clickable again */
  width: 45px;
  height: 40px;
  background-color: rgba(0, 142, 92, 0.8); /* semi-transparent so content can be seen */
  border-radius: 8px;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  justify-content: center;
  padding: 6px;
  cursor: pointer;
}

/* Button lines */
.floating-menu-button .line {
  width: 100%;
  height: 5px;
  background: white;
  margin: 3px 0;
  border-radius: 4px;
}

/* SIDE MENU */
.side-menu {
  position: fixed;
  top: 80px; /* aligns exactly under header */
  left: -230px;
  width: 230px;
  height: calc(100vh - 80px);
  background-color: #008e5c;
  color: white;
  transition: left 0.3s ease;
  padding-top: 20px;
  z-index: 3000;
}

.side-menu.open { left: 0; }

.side-menu ul {
  list-style: none;
  padding: 0;
}

.side-menu li {
  padding: 15px 20px;
  cursor: pointer;
}

.side-menu li:hover {
  background-color: #066e4a;
}

.back-btn {
  background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
  font-weight: bold;
}

/* CONTENT */
.content {
  margin-top: 80px;          /* pushed below header */
  padding: 20px;
  height: calc(100vh - 80px);
  overflow-y: auto;
}


---

üíØ WHAT THIS NOW ACHIEVES

‚úî HEADER hides content when content goes under it

(because it's fixed + solid background)

‚úî FLOATING BUTTON does not block scrolling

because:

wrapper = pointer-events: none

only the button = clickable


‚úî CONTENT SCROLLS behind the floating button

and stays visible because:

floating button is semi-transparent

it is not a scroll blocker


‚úî Absolutely smooth behavior


